  "remarks": "QDe.143. A Tunisian armed group with links to the Organization of Al-Qaida in the Islamic Maghreb (QDe.014). The leader is Seifallah ben Hassine (QDi.333). Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 2368 (2017) was concluded on 4 Dec. 2019. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 2610 (2021) was concluded on 30 October 2023.; Listing: Listed by the 1267 Committee on 23 Sep. 2014 ( amended on 6 Dec. 2019, 30 Oct. 2023 )",
